  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594690/extras/a8b7120f8bf9b3ec0e3baa9d62a45ccc.poster.avif?t=1708626785\" width=620 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594690/extras/a8b7120f8bf9b3ec0e3baa9d62a45ccc.webm?t=1708626785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594690/extras/a8b7120f8bf9b3ec0e3baa9d62a45ccc.mp4?t=1708626785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>A fast-faced speedrunning platformer where you undermine the righteous angel's unrighteous past. Break through the cute, charming aesthetic to find its sinister undertones. It's difficult, but the skill ceiling is high, and when you break through the initial barrier, it's a very rewarding game. Just a warning: this is a game for platforming veterans! Know what you're getting into!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594690/extras/a130c42dd4f492c08a8b21db8c03a320.poster.avif?t=1708626785\" width=608 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594690/extras/a130c42dd4f492c08a8b21db8c03a320.webm?t=1708626785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594690/extras/a130c42dd4f492c08a8b21db8c03a320.mp4?t=1708626785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Master the tricks and the tech in a judgment-free zone. Or, turn on \"mock me\" mode to be insulted when you mess up! Tame your wings and learn to manoeuvre around traps, steel yourself against brambles, dodge and weave around sinister bosses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594690/extras/2d16a755d74c7d8433089340aa91761f.poster.avif?t=1708626785\" width=578 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594690/extras/2d16a755d74c7d8433089340aa91761f.webm?t=1708626785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594690/extras/2d16a755d74c7d8433089340aa91761f.mp4?t=1708626785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br>They're sinister. But also the perfect level of cute so you feel bad about hurting them.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594690/extras/1084a62d8605d6d62454e318511ea955.poster.avif?t=1708626785\" width=596 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594690/extras/1084a62d8605d6d62454e318511ea955.webm?t=1708626785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594690/extras/1084a62d8605d6d62454e318511ea955.mp4?t=1708626785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Forty plus unique, hand-crafted levels<br></li><li>An accessible yet engaging narrative<br></li><li>Five core areas<br></li><li>Secrets and extras (hunt for them if you dare!)<br></li><li>A willingness to sacrifice all my artistic principles for a funny joke <br></li><li>A bona fide title screen (that's right)<br></li><li>An extensive soundtrack to get your blood pumping<br></li><li>Many, many spikes and brambles and explosions and occasionally pits<br></li><li>Skeletons<br></li><li>Closets<br></li><li>Skeletons in closets<br></li><li>A real pause menu for you pro gamers<br></li><li>Configurable settings<br></li><li>A writer who doesn't know how to end a list<br></li><li>Compromising poses<br></li><li>And more!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594690/extras/fdccb3a1e5c3ca9ac893d569c5f536ca.poster.avif?t=1708626785\" width=622 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594690/extras/fdccb3a1e5c3ca9ac893d569c5f536ca.webm?t=1708626785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594690/extras/fdccb3a1e5c3ca9ac893d569c5f536ca.mp4?t=1708626785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594690/extras/a8b7120f8bf9b3ec0e3baa9d62a45ccc.poster.avif?t=1708626785\" width=620 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594690/extras/a8b7120f8bf9b3ec0e3baa9d62a45ccc.webm?t=1708626785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594690/extras/a8b7120f8bf9b3ec0e3baa9d62a45ccc.mp4?t=1708626785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>A fast-faced speedrunning platformer where you undermine the righteous angel's unrighteous past. Break through the cute, charming aesthetic to find its sinister undertones. It's difficult, but the skill ceiling is high, and when you break through the initial barrier, it's a very rewarding game. Just a warning: this is a game for platforming veterans! Know what you're getting into!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594690/extras/a130c42dd4f492c08a8b21db8c03a320.poster.avif?t=1708626785\" width=608 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594690/extras/a130c42dd4f492c08a8b21db8c03a320.webm?t=1708626785\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594690/extras/a130c42dd4f492c08a8b21db8c03a320.mp4?t=1708626785\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Master the tricks and the tech in a judgment-free zone. Or, turn on \"mock me\" mode to be insulted when you mess up! Tame your wings and learn to manoeuvre around traps, steel yourself against brambles, dodge and weave around sinister bosses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\